text: Casanare Department is a department in the central eastern region of Colombia. The capital is Yopal. == Municipalities == These municipalities are in the department: # Aguazul # Chámeza # Hato Corozal # La Salina # Maní # Monterrey # Nunchía # Orocué # Paz de Ariporo # Pore # Recetor # Sabanalarga # Sácama # San Luis de Palenque # Támara # Tauramena # Trinidad # Villanueva # Yopal == Other websites == * Government of Casanare official website Category:Departments of Colombia
